FORGEZERO QUICK START
======================

INSTALL FORGEZERO
-----------------
The shortest path is:
go install github.com/forgezero-cli/ForgeZero/cmd/fz@latest

Verify the install:
fz -v

INITIALIZE A PROJECT
--------------------
mkdir myproject && cd myproject
fz -init

This scaffolds a small project layout with .fz.toml, .fzignore, configure.fz,
and README.

BUILD YOUR FIRST TARGET
-----------------------
fz -dir ./src

Or build a single file:
fz -cc main.c

USEFUL FOLLOW-UPS
-----------------
Read CLI-REFERENCE for the complete option list.
Read TOML_CONFIG for configuration details.
